<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=9895970771321></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9895970771321><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=434&mid=9895970771321>RE: Ummmm me confused about this whole quest</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=434&mid=9895970771321#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, May 11th 12:04 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Okay. Sir Lucan is corrupt, even though he is a Warrior Guildleader. Killing him makes you instantly KOS with Warriors, Rogues, Shadowknights, Necros, and guards whose names start with Guard. BUT it makes you warmly to everyone in the zone with the bank (except for the guards outside of the bank), and the paladin guild, including all guards whose names begin with Sir. The warriors and paladins are on conlficting factions. the lore states that Sir Lucan was a paladin, but was corrupted. He now teaches warriors, and wants the SoulFire for himself. The Paladins want you to get it before him.&nbsp;&nbsp;THis weapon is NODROP, meaning you have to do the quest yourself. Also, it is needed for the Fiery Avenger, which in turn is needed for the Fiery Defender (Paladin Epic Sword). Also, to avoid the corrupt guards, just take the secret entrance to the left of the gate in East Freeport, which leads you through the catacombs and the exit is at the Paladin Guild. The SoulFire itself isnt so great, but you need it for the Fiery Avenger (33/44, +15 STR, +10 CHA, +15 WIS, +25 HP, +25 MANA, +5 SV VS FIRE, POISON, DISEASE, COLD, MAGIC, effect Flame Shock: 110 DD) which is used for the Fiery Defender (35/40, +15 AC, +20 STR, +10 STA, +15 WIS, +70 HP, +30 MANA, +10 SV VS FIRE, POISON, DISEASE, COLD, MAGIC, effect: Holy Shock: 150 DD and a 6 second stun)  Both swords have a Fire Graphic and are 2handed Slashing, Fiery Avenger and SoulFire look the same but Fiery Defender has a unique look. So, every Paladin should have this, and if you are truly a Paladin, you will realize that Sir Lucan is an enemy to all that is right.<br><br>Senwen Holyblade<br>Loyal follower of Tunare on her server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
