	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you would like to get some good info on this quest. Goto www.everlore.com.. Goto quest's by zone.. Goto N.FP.. There is a file called Soul Fire Made even easier.. Will tell you step, by step how and what to do fer this quest.. This does not have any background info, but if you are just lookin to do quest, it's a very good reference.. I completed this quest in 3 days. Day 1 got the hilt, day 2 got 8 people together to keel Sir Lucan,day 3 went and turned in the goodies to get the sword..&nbsp;&nbsp;So, hope this helps, ya if your lookin fer it.. Unless your going after your epic, this really isn't worth the KOS faction you get in E&W Fp for killin guard lucan. The Mith 2hd is just as nice lower, but a much lower delay, or a Wurmslayer hit's harder/faster and you have use of a sheild. Only reason I got this was cuz I'm all about "How it Looks". If anyone know's how to regain faction plz send me an email and let me know.. I have seen people runnin round with flamin swords in FP before.. So, either they didn't take the faction hit or there is a way to regain faction..<br><br>Wolvbane 43rd circle Paladin<br>The Trib<br>"Shared Vision"<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
